aggregate_monthly_data.py: Integration of NEX-GDDP-CMIP6 data from the daily scale to the monthly scale.
merge2time_series.py: Integration of monthly-scale NEX data into a time series from 1950 to 2100.
create_lat_grid.ipynb: Creation of latitude grid data for calculation of potential evapotranspiration (PET).
